# Per-extension patterns below cover the actual data the app writes
# (Hindsight's runtime data lives in %APPDATA%/Hindsight/data/, never inside
# the repo). A bare `data/` rule was previously here but it also matched
# `src/main/data/`, which is real source code (the data adapters live there).
*.bi5
*.parquet
*.duckdb
*.sqlite
*.sqlite-journal
*.sqlite-wal
*.sqlite-shm
